{"about_the_game":"Embark on a perilous journey throughout the lands of Olus with the warrior Lions and his spectral twin Creo. Fulfill their vow to protect each other from the vile forces determined to split them apart in this isometric action adventure game where working together is the key to survival.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescriptionHeader_COMBAT.png?t=1726857571\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescription_COMBAT_Ex.png?t=1726857571\" /><br>Control two characters in tandem to experience co-op gameplay within a single player setting. Seamlessly swap between playstyles to make the most of either characters best attributes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescriptionHeader_EXPLORE.png?t=1726857571\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescription_EXPLORE_Ex.png?t=1726857571\" /><br>Travel together day and night uncovering new paths as the sun sets on each region. Encounter curious and remarkable creatures who may aid or deceive you during the journey.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescriptionHeader_TRAVERSAL.png?t=1726857571\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescription_TRAVERSAL_Ex.png?t=1726857571\" /><br>Dash, launch &amp; jolt at high velocity to cover vast stretches of terrain. Activate spectral bridges shared between the living and the dead to reach places once forgotten.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707630/extras/CustomDescriptionHeader_COMPA